headline: 2025 Dividend Kings - Off To A Strong Start

headline: PPG Board of Directors ranks among top ten in study of governance capacity
summary: PITTSBURGH, February 26, 2025--PPG (NYSE: PPG) today announced that its board of directors ranked in the top ten among the boards of more than 650 American corporations, according to a study of governance capacity that was released by JamesDruryPartners.
